WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:22.000
Take a base cardstock

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:27.000
and fold it in half

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:51.000
stamp the easter set with the basket and cut all that you'll need

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:04.000
trace the basket shape on a cardstock

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:14.000
and then cut it

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:25.000
stamp your greetings with an ink pad and a stamp

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:34.000
smudge the edges with a sponge

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:50.000
now cut another cardstock to place it on the base card

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:20.000
and then place an easter designed paper for the background

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:36.000
look for a suitable position for the pieces

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:55.000
stick the background eggs according with the basket position

00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:11.000
stick the basket using a 3d adhesive

00:03:21.000 --> 00:03:26.000
again with the 3d adhesive, stick the little eggs

00:03:45.000 --> 00:03:48.000
you can decor the card as you want

00:04:23.000 --> 00:04:25.000
Thanx! See you next time!

